data.description: ***Seller is offering $5,000 use as you choose allowance!*** Buy down rates, home improvements, etc!Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-and-a-half bathroom house that exudes both comfort and style. As you enter, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting living area with a fireplace and kitchen with modern appliances which is the heart of this home. Adjacent to the dining area , you'll find a versatile extra space that can be utilized as a formal dining room for hosting elegant dinners, a cozy den for relaxation or functional office for those who work from home. The bedrooms are tucked away in the back providing comfort and privacy for family members and guests.One of the highlights of this property is the beautiful sunroom, seamlessly integrated into the living space. This sun lit sanctuary can be enjoyed year-round, offering a tranquil spot for reading, entertaining, or simply basking in the warmth of natural light.Step outside into the courtyard, and you'll find a built-in pool and above ground spa creating a resort-like atmosphere for relaxation and recreation. Whether you're hosting weekend gatherings or a quiet evening, the outdoor space is sure to be a favorite feature.This house is not just a living space, it's a home.  With its perfect design and outdoor amenities it provides a perfect canvas for you to create lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours!
